item.title: CVE-2024-0239|2024-08-01T17:41:16.028Z -- unknown -- contact%20form%207%20connector
item.description: The Contact Form 7 Connector WordPress plugin before 1.2.3 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against administrators.
